<p>安装:</p>
<p><code>sh ./Anaconda3-2021.05-Linux-x86_64.sh</code><br><img src="/../image/17.jpg"><br><img src="/../image/18.jpg"><br><img src="/../image/19.jpg"><br><img src="/../image/20.jpg"><br><img src="/../image/21.jpg"><br>输入yes后就安装完成了.</p>
